{"tid":644981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇AV仁當年係立法會上意淫女性嘅行為？","createTime":"2018-04-27T16:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T20:21:43.000Z","uid":183588,"like":76,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"884cd9c5ac02d931dfbf1b2df7720f7536cd43d3","tid":644981,"uid":183588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1393333-20180426.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1393333-20180426.htm&d=CeQB9ayxr9xG%2F5Jj959dQP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1370916f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1393333-20180426.htm&h=c4feb3a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1393333-20180426.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n何俊仁認為，許智峯這兩天的道歉不夠真誠，沒有足夠反省，有關行為亦令人感覺許智峯是欺凌和冒犯該名女職員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/001949_bcdc51be984c255db1bb5d109b959ebd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F001949_bcdc51be984c255db1bb5d109b959ebd.png&h=393fcaa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/002041_38f597835e3e8064bbb5788295fe9a9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F002041_38f597835e3e8064bbb5788295fe9a9f.png&h=483e4c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尊重女性，由何俊仁做起。"},{"pid":"837190cb663da16081838e78b70d5b15a92ef905","tid":644981,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e84fdff3bf90a8fd7fa088bb56b2a353ebc57d2","tid":644981,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\ndq 左佢？<br />\n<br />\n咁仲可以靠邊個做反對黨"},{"pid":"c804b87577479a3db311584316c129fbeca7badc","tid":644981,"uid":183588,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"837190cb663da16081838e78b70d5b15a92ef905","tid":644981,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/003601_43ac49c953fdafac5da36d08971fa05f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F003601_43ac49c953fdafac5da36d08971fa05f.png&h=2a2da254&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51eb289afc468d296a17b03ccd376ec1b2d7e71c","tid":644981,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"敬業姐 成日要兩邊跑 搵食唔易呀"},{"pid":"72bde7df1ee351730eaed23a027ac641209a14c9","tid":644981,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"睇下j圖都唔得？"},{"pid":"92bd17593116f853db7d820bdb7f0d027cf32863","tid":644981,"uid":20816,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"大佬，攞埋條j出嚟對住張相打j就話「意淫女性」啫<br />\n睇下相又「意淫女性」，你唔俾佢揀緊新抱？<br />\n班女明星著成咁都係想男人睇，紅咗、多人討論就賺多啲錢<br />\n又要著成咁又要唔俾男人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你最多話佢分心、唔專業，話佢「意淫女性」真係on99<br />\n至於你將佢此舉同許智峰事件相比係不恰當<br />\n1.兩件事性質不同，何俊仁唔會令班女明星不安；<br />\n2.就當何俊仁殺人放火，唔俾佢而家痛改前非？又係啲誰沒有罪才可以出聲嘅on9講法？<br />\n3.又假設佢無悔改，都唔代表佢無權出聲，<br />\n4.何俊仁只係公開睇j圖，如果睇過j圖就無權講「尊重女性」，閣下在時事台公開貼AV截圖亦無權要求人哋「尊重女性」"},{"pid":"39b3e8caac5dcd00c57423d37d9fc8f10434b2de","tid":644981,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"074e32ad7d30b5f54153077f57fc99fdfd2add18","tid":644981,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"屌，seed 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e56b3ca80f699003d0b5e06197a9601de0f034","tid":644981,"uid":56729,"like